    "The schematic diagram of the GA-LSSVM model is illustrated in Fig. 2.",
    "Kennedy and Eberhart 57 initially presented the PSO algorithm as an evolutionary computing method.",
    "Nowadays, the PSO method is frequently utilized in machine learning applications including neural networks, fuzzy control, and functional optimization [58] [59] [60] [61].",
    "PSO algorithm has fewer adjustment parameters than other optimization",
    "techniques as well as the convergence speed is fast, and it is straightforward and simple to implement 54."
